                <h5>Searching for Weather Information</h5>
                <p>Enter the name of a city or location in the search bar and press the search icon to retrieve weather information.</p>
                <br>
                <h5>Understanding Weather Data</h5>
                <p><strong style="font-size: 20px;">Temperature:</strong> Displayed in degrees Celsius (Â°C).</p>
